  <AlienRace.AlienBackstoryDef>
    <defName>LBD_Miraboreasu_Childhood</defName>
    <slot>Childhood</slot>
    <title>禁忌巨兽</title>
    <titleShort>巨兽</titleShort>
    <description>作为不详的象征，黑龙的诞生和其他古龙种一样笼罩在迷雾中，人们对这种超脱于生态系统的巨兽知之甚少，其名字已经成为命运之战的象征。黑龙对自身以外的事物都极度蔑视，不认同任何存在。</description>
    <skillGains>
      <Artistic>-10</Artistic>
      <Plants>-10</Plants>
      <Medicine>-10</Medicine>
      <Animals>-10</Animals>
      <Social>-10</Social>
    </skillGains>
    <!-- <workDisables>ManualDumb,Cooking,Mining</workDisables> -->
    <requiredWorkTags>Violent</requiredWorkTags>
    <spawnCategories>
      <li>LBD_Miraboreasu_Backstory_Categories</li>
    </spawnCategories>
    <bodyTypeGlobal>Thin</bodyTypeGlobal>
    <bodyTypeFemale>Thin</bodyTypeFemale>
    <bodyTypeMale>Thin</bodyTypeMale>
    <forcedTraitsChance>
      <li>
        <defName Degree="0">Greedy</defName>
        <chance>100</chance>
      </li>
      <li>
        <defName Degree="0">Psychopath</defName>
        <chance>100</chance>
      </li>
      <li>
        <defName Degree="0">Bloodlust</defName>
        <chance>100</chance>
      </li>
    </forcedTraitsChance>
    <passions>
      <Intellectual>2</Intellectual>
    </passions>
    <shuffleable>false</shuffleable>
  </AlienRace.AlienBackstoryDef>
  <AlienRace.AlienBackstoryDef>
    <defName>LBD_Miraboreasu_Adulthood</defName>
    <slot>Adulthood</slot>
    <title>毁灭之兆</title>
    <titleShort>黑龙</titleShort>
    <description>传说中，曾经君临于世界的繁荣大国修雷德国，其王都在一夜之间被黑龙毁灭，曾经夸耀荣华的宫殿被付之一炬，以古城为中心的旧王都化为无法感受任何生命气息的不毛之地。黑龙将焚尽后的修雷德城堡作为自己的巢穴，这一带都被视为无法踏足的禁区······</description>
    <skillGains>
      <Intellectual>5</Intellectual>
      <Crafting>5</Crafting>
      <Melee>10</Melee>
      <Shooting>2</Shooting>
      <Mining>5</Mining>
    </skillGains>
    <!-- <workDisables>ManualDumb,Cooking,Mining</workDisables> -->
    <requiredWorkTags>Violent</requiredWorkTags>
    <spawnCategories>
      <li>LBD_Miraboreasu_Backstory_Categories</li>
    </spawnCategories>
    <bodyTypeGlobal>Thin</bodyTypeGlobal>
    <bodyTypeFemale>Thin</bodyTypeFemale>
    <bodyTypeMale>Thin</bodyTypeMale>
    <forcedTraitsChance>
      <li>
        <defName Degree="0">LBD_BlackDragon_Trait</defName>
        <chance>100</chance>
      </li>
      <li>
        <defName Degree="0">Abrasive</defName>
        <chance>100</chance>
      </li>
    </forcedTraitsChance>
    <passions>
      <Shooting>2</Shooting>
      <Crafting>1</Crafting>
    </passions>
    <shuffleable>false</shuffleable>
  </AlienRace.AlienBackstoryDef>
  <TraitDef>
    <defName>LBD_BlackDragon_Trait</defName>
    <commonality>0</commonality>
    <disabledWorkTags>Firefighting</disabledWorkTags>
    <degreeDatas>
      <li>
        <label>黑龙</label>
        <description>{PAWN_nameDef} 是一只上古巨兽——虽然不知道因为什么原因从修雷德废墟掉到了边缘世界，还变成了这副模样。{PAWN_pronoun} 是毁灭的化身，只有面前的蝼蚁陷入火海构成的地狱，才会让{PAWN_pronoun}感到愉悦。</description>
        <theOnlyAllowedMentalBreaks>
          <li>FireStartingSpree</li>
        </theOnlyAllowedMentalBreaks>
        <allowedMeditationFocusTypes><li>Flame</li></allowedMeditationFocusTypes>
        <enablesNeeds>
          <li>Need_LBD_BlackDragon</li>
        </enablesNeeds>
        <disablesNeeds>
          <li>Food</li>
			    <li>Outdoors</li>
        </disablesNeeds>
        <statFactors>
          <StaggerDurationFactor>0</StaggerDurationFactor>
          <IncomingDamageFactor>0.5</IncomingDamageFactor>
          <CaravanBonusSpeedFactor>3</CaravanBonusSpeedFactor>
        </statFactors>
      </li>
    </degreeDatas>
    <exclusionTags>
      <li>Toughness</li>
    </exclusionTags>
  </TraitDef>
</Defs>
